data.description: Come out to see this super cute ready to move in split level home! Over 1,600 sq.ft., a fireplace and 3 bedrooms and 3 baths. Lots of updates have been completed including fresh paint to the interior and the exterior. All hardware has been updated to match inside the home. $2,000 floor allowance, 7 star HSA Home Warranty. Formal dining as well as an eat in kitchen. Partial finish in the basement with lots of storage. 2 car attached garage. Large fenced in yard with a nice deck off the back of the home for all outdoor activites. Established neighborhood close to all things in Ankeny!
